<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Club de Cachorros - Tampa, FL</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --gold: #c5a059;
            --black: #1a1a1a;
            --cream: #fdfaf5;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: var(--cream);
            color: var(--black);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Top Navigation */
        .header-nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px 8%;
            background: white;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gold);
        }

        .logo-text {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .lang-dropdown {
            padding: 8px 15px;
            border: 1px solid var(--gold);
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            background: white;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero-wrap {
            position: relative;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.7), rgba(255,255,255,0.7)), 
                        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554456854-55a063e97cb4?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=2070');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            padding: 100px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .main-card {
            max-width: 850px;
            width: 95%;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border: 4px solid white;
        }

        /* Testimonials Section */
        .testimonials {
            padding: 80px 8%;
            background: white;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            width: 60px;
            height: 3px;
            background: var(--gold);
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -10px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }

        .review-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .review-box {
            background: var(--cream);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-bottom: 4px solid var(--gold);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .review-box:hover { transform: translateY(-10px); }

        .star-rating { color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 1.2rem; }

        /* Footer / Contact */
        .footer-call {
            background: var(--black);
            color: white;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .phone-btn {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: var(--gold);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: block;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .phone-btn:hover { color: white; }

        /* Multi-language Utility */
        .en-content { display: none; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="header-nav">
    <div class="logo-text">Club de <span style="color:var(--gold)">Cachorros</span></div>
    <select class="lang-dropdown" onchange="switchLanguage(this.value)">
        <option value="es">Español 🇪🇸</option>
        <option value="en">English 🇺🇸</option>
    </select>
</header>

<section class="hero-wrap">
    <img src="DF3EE4A4-5740-4788-8960-0D5333BABDAB.png" alt="Club de Cachorros Card" class="main-card">
    
    <div class="es-content"><h1>Cachorros Felices, Familias Felices</h1></div>
    <div class="en-content"><h1>Happy Puppies, Happy Families</h1></div>
</section>

<section class="testimonials">
    <h2 class="es-content section-title">Testimonios de Clientes</h2>
    <h2 class="en-content section-title">What Our Families Say</h2>
    
    <div class="review-container">
        <div class="review-box">
            <div class="star-rating">★★★★★</div>
            <p class="es-content">"Nuestra pequeña Luna ha traído tanta felicidad. ¡Gracias Club de Cachorros!"</p>
            <p class="en-content">"Our little Luna has brought so much happiness. Thank you Club de Cachorros!"</p>
            <strong>Familia Perez</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="review-box">
            <div class="star-rating">★★★★★</div>
            <p class="es-content">"El cuidado y la profesionalidad son increíbles. Súper recomendados."</p>
            <p class="en-content">"The care and professionalism are incredible. Highly recommended."</p>
            <strong>Carlos M.</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="review-box">
            <div class="star-rating">★★★★★</div>
            <p class="es-content">"Una experiencia maravillosa. El criadero es impecable y muy limpio."</p>
            <p class="en-content">"A wonderful experience. The breeding area is impeccable and very clean."</p>
            <strong>Ana L.</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="review-box">
            <div class="star-rating">★★★★★</div>
            <p class="es-content">"Encontramos a nuestro mejor amigo aquí. Sano, feliz y juguetón."</p>
            <p class="en-content">"We found our best friend here. Healthy, happy, and playful."</p>
            <strong>The Thompsons</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="review-box">
            <div class="star-rating">★★★★★</div>
            <p class="es-content">"Excelente servicio de principio a fin. El veterinario quedó impresionado."</p>
            <p class="en-content">"Excellent service from start to finish. Our vet was impressed."</p>
            <strong>Jessica K.</strong>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<footer class="footer-call">
    <p class="es-content">¿Listo para conocer a tu nuevo mejor amigo? Llámanos hoy:</p>
    <p class="en-content">Ready to meet your new best friend? Call us today:</p>
    <a href="tel:8632770168" class="phone-btn">863-277-0168</a>
    <p>Tampa, FL | Club de Cachorros</p>
</footer>

<script>
    function switchLanguage(lang) {
        const es = document.querySelectorAll('.es-content');
        const en = document.querySelectorAll('.en-content');
        
        if (lang === 'en') {
            es.forEach(el => el.style.display = 'none');
            en.forEach(el => el.style.display = 'block');
        } else {
            es.forEach(el => el.style.display = 'block');
            en.forEach(el => el.style.display = 'none');
        }
    }
</script>

</body>
</html>
